description:
OK, it's round three of the Jerk Off Contest series and this time we have Brian, Luke, Adam, and Josh. As you probably know, the object of the contest is to see which of the four contestants can shoot the farthest. The trusty cum table makes another appearance, and now it has a very nice black surface so you can see every drop.
I really enjoyed filming this because the guys really seem to click and they joke and smile a lot.
This contest was hard to judge because two of the guys shoot clear over the table.That being the case, I had to make my judgement based on a secondary factor - volume. So see if you agree with my decision...
title: Jerk Off Contest 3
